timal construction; if $\\gcd(M,k)=2$,\nthen there are two optimal constructions; and if $\\gcd(M,k)\\geq 3$, then there\nare at most two optimal constructions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 24 Apr 2010 12:52:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-04-29"}
